A type for the Facility element that is the root of a COBie document. Facility contains information about the facility being exchanged during a given COBie deliverable. Since COBie deliverables may be exchanged during planning, design, construction, handover, or operation phases there may be differences in facility designations. COBie files will typically contain a single facility. Facility is a named distinct operational built or geographic asset, typically a building or section of infrastructure along with details and extent of the geographic site and of the temporal project
